Sentencas: Single phase La0.75Sr0.25Mn0.5Cr0.5-xO3-delta(LSCMT, 0 <= x <= 0.3) perovskites were investigated as possible anode material for solid oxide fuel cells with yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte.
Titulo: Effects of Ti doping on the electrochemical performance of (La0.75Sr0.25)(Mn0.5Cr0.5)O3-δ anode for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: LSCMT samples were synthesized by solid state reaction method and sintered at 1500 degrees C in air Rietveld refinement of X-ray powder diffraction data show that the LSCMT materials crystallize in the rhombohedral symmetry with R (3) over barC space group.
Titulo: Effects of Ti doping on the electrochemical performance of (La0.75Sr0.25)(Mn0.5Cr0.5)O3-δ anode for solid oxide fuel cells
